  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/bbaf7aa4484c03690eac075254fedfa5.poster.avif?t=1672784119\" width=472 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/bbaf7aa4484c03690eac075254fedfa5.webm?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/bbaf7aa4484c03690eac075254fedfa5.mp4?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Adventure Like No Other</h2>January, 1928. The SS Carolina is lost deep in the ocean. There's a deadly chill outside. The captain is hiding something from you. By night 2 you're attacked and the crew is missing! It's a nightmare!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/3d4e6e7125dcb5172ac3ad43cb40e9ed.poster.avif?t=1672784119\" width=472 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/3d4e6e7125dcb5172ac3ad43cb40e9ed.webm?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/3d4e6e7125dcb5172ac3ad43cb40e9ed.mp4?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You play as 2nd Officer Walton. Explore the ship, use items, find the crew, and try to survive! You must get back to land and not let the ship sink.<br><br>This is a completely new experience from the creators of SimAirport and SimCasino!<br><br><strong>Art by lunaanandi</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/d989ca12750ee35ec63261bdce957738.poster.avif?t=1672784119\" width=472 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/d989ca12750ee35ec63261bdce957738.webm?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/d989ca12750ee35ec63261bdce957738.mp4?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A point and click adventure game with a horror twist!<br></li><li>Beautiful, retro pixel art style with a nautical theme!<br></li><li>Hunt for crucial items and use them to survive and rid the curse!<br></li><li>Classically designed logical game mechanics with a modern UI for a satisfying experience.<br></li><li>Discover the truth and unlock multiple endings!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/bbaf7aa4484c03690eac075254fedfa5.poster.avif?t=1672784119\" width=472 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/bbaf7aa4484c03690eac075254fedfa5.webm?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/bbaf7aa4484c03690eac075254fedfa5.mp4?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Adventure Like No Other</h2>January, 1928. The SS Carolina is lost deep in the ocean. There's a deadly chill outside. The captain is hiding something from you. By night 2 you're attacked and the crew is missing! It's a nightmare!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/3d4e6e7125dcb5172ac3ad43cb40e9ed.poster.avif?t=1672784119\" width=472 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/3d4e6e7125dcb5172ac3ad43cb40e9ed.webm?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/3d4e6e7125dcb5172ac3ad43cb40e9ed.mp4?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You play as 2nd Officer Walton. Explore the ship, use items, find the crew, and try to survive! You must get back to land and not let the ship sink.<br><br>This is a completely new experience from the creators of SimAirport and SimCasino!<br><br><strong>Art by lunaanandi</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/d989ca12750ee35ec63261bdce957738.poster.avif?t=1672784119\" width=472 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/d989ca12750ee35ec63261bdce957738.webm?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/d989ca12750ee35ec63261bdce957738.mp4?t=1672784119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A point and click adventure game with a horror twist!<br></li><li>Beautiful, retro pixel art style with a nautical theme!<br></li><li>Hunt for crucial items and use them to survive and rid the curse!<br></li><li>Classically designed logical game mechanics with a modern UI for a satisfying experience.<br></li><li>Discover the truth and unlock multiple endings!</li></ul>",
